snippet.title: Reverse Collapse: CodeName Bakery Girl -面包房少女- Features and Gameplay!
snippet.description:
Hello world and today I bring you guys more a video review of Code Name Bakery Girl. NO this is not some cooking game nor is it related to anything bakery but rather a spin off title of Girls Frontline, or rather girls front line before girls frontline exist, this is the game that lead to the development of girls front line, it's a very nice turn based strategy game utilize a lot of stealth ambush elements in the game play. 

Like and Subscribe!
